title: 02/22/22 DPS Best Of - Rob Parker & Mike Harmon Guest Hosting
itunes:title: 02/22/22 DPS Best Of - Rob Parker & Mike Harmon Guest Hosting
description:
Rob Parker and Mike Harmon, in for Dan, react to Juwan Howard getting a 5-game suspension for his actions after Michigan's loss to Wisconsin. The guys dive into Aaron Rogers' cryptic Instagram post and discuss what they think will happen next for the reigning MVP. 10-year NBA Veteran Ryan Hollins joins the guys to preview the second half of the season.
